review: Got my root canal treatment here. Good Experience, Dr. Rachel is friendly, helpful, very professional and easy to talk to. She took us through the entire procedure in detail. Very happy with the treatment and hospitality. Thank you!!!

A casual visit to a dentist  turned into taking her services, which I found to be very high quality. Dr.Rachel has done an excellent job on my teeth which my regular or should I say my previous dentist was not able to. 
She diagnosed my problem very accurately and gave me treatment which was painless and explained me well about the whole procedure. Dr. Rachel is very good at her work. I am going to recommend her to people I know. Keep up the good work my friend. Cheers.
Dr.Rachel is very friendly. She explained everything very patiently . She has treated me and my mother very well. Happy with her service. I recommend Dr Rachel
I visited Dr. Rachel for my severe tooth ache. Doctor and staff are very friendly. Dr. Rachel has treated me with utmost care . I really recommend her for any dental issues. Thankyou
